extends ../layout

block title
  title Jascha Ehrenreich, Magically Shifting Paradigms

block content
  section.author(itemprop='author' itemscope itemtype='http://schema.org/Person')

    .affiliations.list(itemprop='affiliations')
      h4(itemprop='contentType') Organizations
      .disclaimer
        | Groups i am proud to be a part of.
      ul
        li(
          itemprop='memberOf'
          itemscope 
          itemtype='http://schema.org/Organization'
        )
          header
            h5
              a(
                href='http://bwb.is'
                target='bwb' 
                itemprop='legalName'
              ) Bitcoiners Without Borders
          .content
            a(
              href='https://bwb.is'
              target='bwb'
              itemprop='url'
            )
              img(
                itemprop='logo'
                src='/img/bwb.png'
                alt='Bitcoiners Without Borders'
              )
            .description(itemprop='description') 
              | We are a tribe of individuals tired of the destructive trip,
              | workin' on a better day.

        li(
          itemprop='memberOf'
          itemscope
          itemtype='http://schema.org/Organization'
        )
          header
            h5
              a(
                href='https://metalab.at'
                target='utopia'
                itemprop='legalName'
              ) Metalab

          .content
            a(
              href='https://metalab.at'
              target='utopia'
              itemprop='url'
            )
              img(
                itemprop='logo'
                src='/img/metalab.png'
                alt='metalab.at'
              )
            .description(
              itemprop='description'
            ) 
              | The Metalab is 
              s the
              |  a 
              a(
                itemprop='' 
                href='http://hackerspaces.org/wiki/'
              ) hackspace
              |  in 
              span(
                itemprop='contactPoint'
              ) Vienna, Austria.
              |  Chances are high that i am sitting in the 
              span Metalab lounge
              |  at this moment, 
              | which means that i am at the exact position of the orange dot you can see on  
              a(
                href='http://www.openstreetmap.org/node/254344537' 
                target='utopia'
                itemprop='contactPoint'
              ) Openstreetmap



    .projects.list
      header 
        h4(itemprop='contentType') Projects:
      .disclaimer
        | Those are some of the projects i worked on and want to endorse.
      ul
        li(
          itemprop='brand'
          itemscope
          itemtype='http://schema.org/Product'
        )
          header
            h5
              a(
                href='http://magicshifter.net'
                target='_blank'
                itemprop='legalName'
              ) MagicShifter - the Open Source Magic Lamp!

          .content
            a(
              href='http://magicshifter.net'
              target='_blank'
              itemprop='url'
            )
              img(
                itemprop='image' 
                src='/img/magicshifter-logo.png' 
                alt='magicshifter.net'
              )

            .description(
              itemprop='description' 
              itemscope itemtype='http://schema.org/Organisation'
            ) 
              | An open source hardware gadget for lighting, gaming,
              | and persistence of vision applications.
              | Charge and reprogram it over usb!
              | Get one of the limited first batch
              span(itemprop='affiliate')
                a(
                  itemprop='url'
                  target='hackerspaceshop'
                  href='http://www.hackerspaceshop.com/magicshifter.html' 
                ) 
                  span(itemprop='legalName') @hackerspaceshop
              
              |.  The MagicShifter was created by 
              a.person(
                itemprop='colleague' 
                href='https://metalab.at/wiki/Benutzer:Wizard23' 
                target='wizard23'
              ) Philipp Tiefenbacher
              | .
              .testimonial 
                | Every sufficiently advanced technology is indistinguishable from a MagicShifter
                p.author Arthur C. Clarke, Proud Owner

        li(itemprop='brand' itemscope itemtype='http://schema.org/Product')
          header
            h5
              a(
                itemprop='legalName' 
                href='https://github.com/metalab/screeninvader' 
                target='utopia'
              ) Screeninvader

          .content
            a(
              itemprop='url' 
              href='https://github.com/metalab/screeninvader' 
              target='utopia' 
            )
              img(
                itemprop='image' 
                src='/img/screeninvader-logo.png' 
                alt='Screeninvader'
              )

            .description(itemprop='description')
              | Ever wished you could play media content from your device on any screen or projector in just an instant? This is what ScreenInvader helps you do. Most of the hard work was done by
              span(itemprop='colleague')
                a.person(
                  itemscope='url' 
                  href='http://viel-zu.org' 
                  target='kallaballa'
                ) 
                  span(itemprop='name') Amir Hassan

                | . Check out his 
                a(
                  href='https://github.com/kallaballa?tab=repositories' 
                  target='_blank'
                ) github
                |  to see a heap of his ingeniously crazy projects.


